embeds.title: ◈ Jewel☆Star's Server Rules
embeds.description:
⠀
**◈ Follow Discord's TOS and be 18+**
If you're found to be any younger, you'll be kicked immediately following the server's TOS.

**◈ Use common sense**
There are rules but like... if you have common sense, these shouldn't even have to be said.

**◈ Be respectful**
Harassment, witch hunting, sexism, racism, homophobia, or any amount of hate speech will be tolerated.

**◈ Avoid offensive remarks,**messages, nicknames, and anything that a reasonable person might find offensive.

**◈ Keep Drama off the server**
I don't need that stuff here...

**◈ Avoid political topics**
I don't need that stuff here either...

**◈ No spamming**
This includes but is not limited too, loud/obnoxious noises in voice, @ mention spam, character spam, image spam, and message spam.

**◈ No Gore or scary content**
For example; screamer links, anything horror related, or death.

**◈ Keep all the lewd stuff in the lewd channels**
Ask me, the admins, or the mods for the R-18 role.

**◈ No harassment**
Including sexual harassment or encouraging of harassment.

**◈ Please make use of the appropriate channels**

**◈ No self or user bots**
These are in some cases against the discord TOS and if you need a bot for something use one of the bots already in the server.

**◈ Swearing is allowed**
Though this does not mean it's okay to be a douchebag to people.

**◈ If you see something against the rules or something that makes you feel unsafe, let staff know.**
We want this server to be a welcoming space!

**◈ Envy is exempt from all rules** and may make exemptions.

**◈ If you don’t like Zikoure,** unspeakable things may occur.

**◈ There may be situations not covered by the rules or times where rules may not fit the situation.**
If this happens the moderators are trusted to handle the situation appropriately.


**By reacting with⠀🔴⠀in the dropdown menu below, you agree to follow the above rules.**
If you refuse, you'll be kicked out immediately.
